# Booking Feature

Modular booking system for service-based businesses.

## Structure
- `models.py`: Concrete models inheriting from `codex_django.booking`.
- `selectors.py`: Business logic wrappers.
- `views.py`: API endpoints.

## Setup
1. Add `features.booking` to `INSTALLED_APPS`.
2. Include `features.booking.urls` in `core.urls`.
3. Configure `Master` profiles in the admin cabinet.
